About Us

Pixel is a technical event organized by the computer science department of Shah and anchor kutchhi engineering college, Chembur Our event aim is to develop an interest in upcoming technologies and motivates them in pursuing a career in such fields Gaining perspectives from established industry leaders will help students to broaden their horizons Speakers' experiences and skills will help chisel the minds of the candidates to help in their corporate and entrepreneurial endeavors.
